# Football Events Frontend - Environment Configuration

# API URL Configuration
# Leave empty for auto-detection (recommended for development)
# The app will automatically detect the protocol (http/https) and hostname

# For explicit configuration, uncomment and set:
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:3001/api/v1

# Production example (HTTPS):
# VITE_API_URL=https://api.yourdomain.com/api/v1

# Mobile development (use your computer's IP):
# VITE_API_URL=http://192.168.1.100:3001/api/v1
